{"tid":2116042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4曾報案傷者投訴與疑犯同處一室 7‧21認人：警疑犯面前讀全名","createTime":"2020-07-20T02:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T03:07:36.000Z","uid":53379,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ca72f7ee05219c5e1dabe40c26be596ab72a6856","tid":2116042,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T02:12:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">4曾報案傷者投訴與疑犯同處一室 7‧21認人：警疑犯面前讀全名</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20200720/s00007/1403c3aba6eb04509f95aae585f67491.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20200720%2Fs00007%2F1403c3aba6eb04509f95aae585f67491.jpg&h=802fa3a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7．21傷者之一、立法會議員林卓廷在市民傳給他的片段截圖中，找到逾10個涉嫌參與襲擊市民的白衣人，片段中部分人的容貌清晰可辨，但林卓廷指自片段曝光至今近半年，警方並沒有聯絡他請求提供片段，質疑警方是否有心繼續調查。（鍾林枝攝）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20200720/s00002/1595183446738/4曾報案傷者投訴與疑犯同處一室-7-21認人-警疑犯面前讀全名\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200720%2Fs00002%2F1595183446738%2F4%E6%9B%BE%E5%A0%B1%E6%A1%88%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E8%88%87%E7%96%91%E7%8A%AF%E5%90%8C%E8%99%95%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%A4-7-21%E8%AA%8D%E4%BA%BA-%E8%AD%A6%E7%96%91%E7%8A%AF%E9%9D%A2%E5%89%8D%E8%AE%80%E5%85%A8%E5%90%8D&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zceYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=95d425ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200720%2Fs00002%2F1595183446738%2F4%E6%9B%BE%E5%A0%B1%E6%A1%88%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E8%88%87%E7%96%91%E7%8A%AF%E5%90%8C%E8%99%95%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%A4-7-21%E8%AA%8D%E4%BA%BA-%E8%AD%A6%E7%96%91%E7%8A%AF%E9%9D%A2%E5%89%8D%E8%AE%80%E5%85%A8%E5%90%8D&h=4bc46d31\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20200720/s00002/1595183446738/4曾報案傷者投訴與疑犯同處一室-7-21認人-警疑犯面前讀全名</a>"},{"pid":"12936f127fa7a33925e545c09c2f3f5799b07d61","tid":2116042,"uid":49329